X-WR-CALDESC:Pre-launch SEO check-ins, PH launch day playbook, and ongoing data maintenance for the TruNorth app.
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/Chicago

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-seo-checkin-2-friday@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260605T140000Z
DTEND:20260605T141500Z
SUMMARY:🔎 SEO check-in #2 (GSC + Bing)
DESCRIPTION:Open Google Search Console → Indexing → Sitemaps & Pages. Look for: sitemap "Success" status, indexed-count climbing, no soft-404s. Then check Bing Webmaster too. 5 min.
LOCATION:https://search.google.com/search-console
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:SEO check-in #2 — 5 min in Search Console
TRIGGER:-PT15M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-seo-checkin-3-monday@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260608T140000Z
DTEND:20260608T141500Z
SUMMARY:🔎 SEO check-in #3 (full week of GSC data)
DESCRIPTION:By now you should have a week of real data. Performance tab → check Impressions / Clicks trends. Pages tab → indexed count should be climbing. If "Discovered – not indexed" plateaus, request indexing on top 10 brand pages manually.
LOCATION:https://search.google.com/search-console
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:-PT15M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-app-store-submission@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260617T140000Z
DTEND:20260617T160000Z
SUMMARY:🍎 Submit to Apple App Store
DESCRIPTION:Target submission date (gives ~5-day Apple review buffer before PH launch Jun 23). Use App Store Connect. Follow /docs/producthunt/LAUNCH_DAY_PLAYBOOK.md prep steps. Have metadata + screenshots ready.
LOCATION:https://appstoreconnect.apple.com
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:-PT1H
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-ph-prelaunch-1week@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260616T140000Z
DTEND:20260616T143000Z
SUMMARY:🚀 PH launch — 1 week out checklist
DESCRIPTION:1-week-out prep:
 • Fire L-10 trade press pitches (/docs/trade-press-pitches.md)
 • Confirm PH subscriber count > goal
 • Twitter pinned tweet live (L-1)
 • LinkedIn pinned post live (L-2)
 • Demo video recorded + uploaded to PH (L-9)
 • Email blast list ready (L-3)
 • Apple App Store status confirmed
LOCATION:https://www.producthunt.com/products/trunorth
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:-PT30M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-ph-launch-eve@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260623T000000Z
DTEND:20260623T010000Z
SUMMARY:🌙 PH launch eve — final readiness
DESCRIPTION:Night before launch (7pm CDT Jun 22):
 • Pre-schedule launch-day Twitter (D-2) for 2:05 AM
 • Pre-schedule launch-day LinkedIn (D-3) for 2:05 AM
 • Draft First Comment (D-1) — paste-ready
 • Test alarm for 1:50 AM
 • Phone fully charged, coffee maker set
 • Re-read /docs/producthunt/LAUNCH_DAY_PLAYBOOK.md
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:-PT0M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:trunorth-ph-launch-hour@trunorthapp.com
DTSTAMP:20260603T120000Z
DTSTART:20260623T065000Z
DTEND:20260623T070000Z
SUMMARY:☕🚀 PH LAUNCH WAKE-UP (1:50 AM CDT)
DESCRIPTION:Launch fires at 2:01 AM CDT (12:01 AM PT). You have 11 minutes to:
 1. Boot up, coffee on
 2. Have First Comment in clipboard
 3. PH dashboard open
 4. Twitter + LinkedIn scheduled posts armed
 5. Phone notifications on for comments
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:AUDIO
TRIGGER:-PT0M
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:-PT10M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

